<exercise id="fs-id1167067070754" class="os-exercise"><problem id="fs-id1167066880913"><!--<para id="fs-id1167067153323"><link class="os-embed" url="#ost/api/ex/k12phys-ch08-ex035"/></para>-->
<para id="fs-id1164566893934">Under what condition(s) is the angular momentum of a system conserved?</para>
<list id="fs-id1164564856357" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-alpha">
<item>When net torque is zero</item>
<item>When net torque is not zero</item>
<item>When moment of inertia is constant</item>
<item>When both moment of inertia and angular momentum are constant</item>
</list>
</problem></exercise>

