<title>Test Prep Extended Response</title>
<exercise id="fs-id1167067132955" class="os-exercise"><problem id="fs-id1167067031224"><!--<para id="fs-id1167066992435"><link class="os-embed" url="#ost/api/ex/k12phys-ch08-ex037"/></para>-->

<para id="fs-id1164562442064">Why does a figure skater spin faster if he pulls his arms and legs in?</para>
<list id="fs-id1164561205436" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-alpha">
<item>Due to an increase in moment of inertia</item>
<item>Due to an increase in angular momentum</item>
<item>Due to conservation of linear momentum</item>
<item>Due to conservation of angular momentum</item>
</list>
